Tran initially gained mainstream exposure as the girlfriend of R&B singer Chris Brown before extending her resume to include modeling and acting .
From 2013 to 2016 , she starred as Vivian Johnson in the web series The Bay .
She is currently managed by Jacob York of Electric Republic .
She is currently represented legally by attorney Patrick Blood .
